									<div class="summary">
						<p>A PHP stream-based socket adapter.</p>
					</div>
				
									<div class="description">
						<p>This stream adapter provides the required method implementations of the abstract <code>Socket</code> class
for the <code>open()</code>, <code>close()</code>, <code>read()</code>, <code>write()</code>, <code>timeout()</code> <code>eof()</code> and <code>encoding()</code> methods.</p>
